agent will not be used on crp land this year because it does not 
achieve the quick knockdown of grasshoppers needed to protect 
nearby crops 
the assessments were said to cover effects on human health 
endangered species other wildlife water resources aquatic 
species soil vegetation air quality land use cultural 
resources and economic concerns 
