publication and give employees a 60day notice 
kheel said workers would be paid during the 60 days but the 
paper could cease publication immediately on sept 15 
he said 17 million is the amount the post hopes to save through 
costcutting measures affecting its unions with the rest to be 
made up in other ways 
the allied is an umbrella group for the 10 unions representing 
900 employees at the post which is the nations oldest daily the 
