almost unbearable the men never know the exact temperature and 
perhaps thats a blessing 
we dont know what day what month what time it is said 
lance cpl eddie zazueta 21 of los angeles i think maybe i was 
supposed to get out last year this is the twilight zone 
under a pounding sun zazueta and his fellow marines patrol the 
