a 50caliber machine gun on the roof just across from a region 
thats been bristling with iraqi troops since the aug 2 invasion 
of kuwait 
the man on gun watch wakes the others up around 5 am 
you usually just smack them in the legs said sgt thomas 
hixson 23 of kingston tenn the section leader for two vehicles 
