and they are back on the line 
the morning bath is perfunctory but important a nearby army 
unit that skipped it came down with body lice and dysentery hixson 
said 
hot showers back at the base come about every 10 days 
breakfast is a banana apple orange or an mre 
mealreadytoeat frankfurters are the favorite 
by 6 am theyve picked up their four gallons of water and are 
headed for the days practice battle positions and maneuvers until 
noon 
at 7 am its 85 degrees an hour later its 97 by noon its 
approaching 120 degrees and the heavy guns crawl under camouflage 
tents until 5 pm 
sleep at midday is impossible because of the heat 
we talk about john waynekinda stuff what to do if were 
attacked said hixson 
we pray for war said zazueta 
