<TEXT>
chancellor helmut kohl plans to name 
four leading east germans to his cabinet to help deal with the 
massive problems of their people when the two germanys merge next 
month government sources said today 
east german prime minister lothar de maiziere is a top candidate 
for a cabinet post said the sources who spoke on condition of 
anonymity 
in east berlin today officials said the number of east germans 
either unemployed or working shorter hours at lower pay jumped to 
nearly 2 million of the 88 million workers last month 
the central labor office said 361286 east germans were without 
jobs last month up by 86269 from the end of july the jobless 
rate went from 31 percent to 41 percent 
that compares with a 16 percent rate at the end of june just 
before east germany converted to a free market economy on july 1 
after four decades of socialism 
many factories and businesses no longer subsidized are having 
difficulty competing with more efficient western enterprises that 
now have access to the east german market electronics textiles 
automotive and agricultural industries are among the hardest hit 
the number of workers who came under a west germanfinanced 
program fighting the rise in unemployment was up to 1439412 more 
than double the 656277 in july 
the workers under this program would have been laid off but are 
being kept on payrolls at shorter hours and lower pay subsidized by 
west germany 
critics say these workers some of whom are making only a small 
amount over the unemployment rate and not actually doing any work 
should be counted among the jobless 
government sources in bonn said today that as part of kohls 
plans for an interim government for a united germany the chancellor 
will be adding four east german officials to his cabinet 
east germany and its government will cease to exist on oct 3 
the chosen day of unity 
the four new ministers will help kohl govern what is now east 
germany between the day of unity and dec 2 when an allgerman 
parliament will be elected said the sources 
they said that along with de maiziere other top candidates are 
guenther krause de maizieres leading unity negotiatior sabine 
bergmannpohl president of the east german parliament and rainer 
ortleb head of the east german free democrats 
the four new cabinet members would be ministers without 
portfolios said the sources 
west german radio said the four new ministers would act as 
intermediaries between kohls government and east germanys five 
soontoberecreated states 
east germany will also have parliamentary representation in the 
interim period between unity and allgerman elections 
the two germanys have agreed 144 east german lawmakers will have 
seats in the west german parliament after unity 
the major east german parties are choosing the 144 on the basis 
of the current balance of power within the east german parliament 
which will be dissolved when unity comes 
