compound in saudi arabia according to the husband of an air force 
sergeant sent to the region 
female soldiers are now being permitted to wear shorts in their 
offduty hours within their living area they also may wear bathing 
suits when swimming in a portable pool at the compound 
servicewomen whould be given that much leeway at every military 
installation in saudi arabia 
theres a chance that any change in the rules would not sit well 
with the saudis this is a country after all where women must use 
separate beaches cover most of their faces in public and are not 
permitted to drive but one can be respectful of national 
custom without demeaning ones own citizens in their mutual 
efforts to keep iraqi troops at bay americans and saudi arabians 
are obliged to show understanding of the others culture 
