cabinet meeting news reports said communications minister raphael 
pinchasi of shas won shamirs promise that the fraud probe against 
deri would be carried out quickly before it could upset the 
political balance 
shas has five seats in the 120member parliament but is a key 
player among the 10 parties in shamirs government it brought down 
shamirs coalition with the labor party on march 15 by abstaining 
in a vote of no confidence 
wiretaps also were featured in the watergate scandal that drove 
richard nixon from the presidency in 1974 
