movements ranks 
the trade unions national commission at its weekly meeting in 
gdansk voted 2621 with 12 abstentions to take away the union logo 
from the gazeta wyborcza newspaper a newspaper spokeswoman later 
said it would comply with the decision 
solidarity chairman lech walesa was not present for the vote 
