trials that have scarred your people dragged into conflicts 
which have torn your communities and wounded too many families 
now the path of reconciliation and harmony has opened before 
you he said you have made a beginning speed up the pace and 
may no one hesitate to rediscover the fraternal path so that your 
hills never again experience division and violence 
burundi a small mountainous nation of 6 million people which 
