but people scuffle to get into line for it two policemen with 
automatic weapons enforce the closing of the doors at 1 pm 
there should be preference for babies said a toothless 
father who had waited five hours in vain with his thin 3monthold 
daughter in his arms 
she hasnt eaten today 
