<TEXT>
in a land of famine and war the 
privileged few feast and frolic 
of ethiopias 50 million people one in 15 faces starvation and 
at least 8 million are trapped in areas being contested by 
government and rebel armies at the other extreme are the 2000 
diplomats and expatriates and a few hundred rich ethiopian 
families 
although rebels of the tigre peoples liberation front have 
advanced to within 100 miles of addis ababa there are no signs of 
panic among foreigners 
they play roulette at the ghion casino order lobster or salmon 
at the jacaranda restaurant play tennis or swim at the hilton 
hotel get together in a steady round of cocktail parties and spend 
weekends at lakeside resorts a few hours drive away 
for most expatriates and ethiopians with hard currency all 
roads lead to the stateowned victory store a fantasyland of 
luxuries on the outskirts far from the pickpockets beggars 
urchins and hawkers who hound shoppers in downtown addis ababa 
its open to anyone with who has dollars in this oneparty 
state whose leaders preached marxism until recently 
other state stores are short of basics like sugar cooking oil 
and rice the victory has french cheeses italian wines danish 
hams tunisian sardines american cookies and ketchup australian 
canned fruits and vegetables and belgian pates 
it also stocks french perfumes spanish shoes japanese 
television sets and video recorders and british refrigerators and 
stoves 
shoppers can relax over coffee or a beer in the victorys own 
red lion pub while their bills are totaled or scan the bulletin 
board for what departing diplomats and others have to offer from 
cars or compact disc players for sale to houses for rent 
foreigners often spend more here in a day than we get in a 
year said an ethiopian clerk at the victory who earns the 
equivalent of about 60 a month its difficult to keep a smile 
when were serving them 
a jewelbedecked woman led four loaded carts out of the store 
a months groceries worth more than 900 she tipped the ethiopians 
who pushed the carts 1 each 
