<TEXT>
thirty years ago the joke 
circulating mgm studio went like this 
too bad about ann miller 
why what happened to her 
she fell down and broke her hair 
the sophisticates used to deride miller with her laquered hair 
powdered face and sunshiny verve but most of her detractors are 
