as the trademark piano received a final 
tuning sales help scurried around the new nordstrom inc 
department store unpacking the remaining boxes rearranging clothes 
racks and getting to know the inventory 
the opening of the nordstrom store at the garden state plaza 
shopping mall in paramus nj marks the retailers first foray 
